@jobinmat: Both shows were regular, but interest dropped down so much that I could not even consider to put them back. 
One episode got SIX DOWNLOADS. With you, now I probably would have seven.

Past is past.

@dark_defender: I got Iron Monkey on same day - two days ago. It would be encoded, as you said: "when you can"...

Deadwood - as any other TV serials - stay out of the question. I haven't mentioned that because I was thinking that you would figured that out yourself - asking some uploader who states "I do not take requests right now because I can't do all stuff" about TV show widely available - is not ... well... "recommended".

My definition of "properly placed request" differs not, even in slightest detail, from ANY request in your life. About something that somebody else should give you for free, even without knowing you at all.
